data.name: DescriptionPageTextStep1Description2
data.value: Ina whakahaere koe i te taupānga, ka waihanga, ka penapena hoki i tētahi ID ingoamuna ki ia waea atamai. Kāore e whiwhi tēnei taupānga i ngā mōhiohio e pā ana ki te tūmataitinga pēnei i te tau waea me te mōhiohio tauwāhi.

data.name: DescriptionPageTextStep2Description2
data.value: I te wā e haere ana te taupānga, ka taea e ētahi atu waea atamai te tāhopu i ngā Tautuhinga ingoamuna o ngā wiki e rua. Ka mukua ngā pūkete tawhito ake i te 2 wiki, ā, ka hurihia te ID ingoamuna hei pare i te tūmataitinga.

data.name: DescriptionPageTextStep3Description1
data.value: Ka whiwhi ētahi atu kaiwhakamahi i tētahi rārangi o ngā Tt ingoamuna o ngā mea tōrunga. I muri i te tango, ka ōrite te pūkete hoapā i hopukina ki te waea atamai. Ki te kore te hua o te ōrite, ka whakamōhio atu ki tō waea atamai me te whakamōhio atu i a koe i ngā hohenga e hiahiatia ana e hiahia ana koe ki te whakahoahoa.
